<plot>Bury It tells the tale of a blind football fanatic who along with his over zealous father, stumble across a group of builders playing a five a side football match. The builders are not amused until, Psycho the leader of the gang invites the imposters to play. The father and son soon realize that Psycho's intentions are not as friendly as they first appeared, and that they are going to have to do more than just play football to get through this game.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087345</url></doc>
